urls.title: What are the Key Facts About Coronavirus?
urls.description: Coronavirus is a family of viruses that can cause the common cold or other more severe diseases such as the new coronavirus disease COVID-19, Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS), and Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS).
